  <summary date="2020-10-21T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Ensuring Access to COVID-19 Vaccines for Seniors Act

This bill specifies that vaccines for COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) that are authorized for emergency use must be covered under Medicare without cost-sharing.

The bill applies retroactively.</summary>
